metadata.name: under the coconut tree
metadata.description:
'under the coconut tree' is an original 1/1 digital illustration by Savannah0ney. 

inspired by a life in the tropics and the calm of sitting under a tree watching the day flow by.

this piece includes both a 1/1 NFT and a 603x603mm physical counterpart available as a package deal to its collector at primary sale.
